---
title: Cheesy Brie and Beef Burgers with Garlic Rosemary Foil-Pouch Potatoes
description: Get ready to hit the grill with ooey-gooey cheesy burgers! Elevate your tastebuds with rosemary-studded patties topped with brie and fig jam. An elegant side of garlic-grilled potatoes rounds off this long weekend winner!
